title: #220 - Content Court: TikTok Pranksters
description:
On this episode of the H3 Podcast the gang hauls in all the usual suspects for a lineup- YouTube's legendary pranksters, and an unexpected surprise suspect, have found a second wind on TikTok and we're here to put em on trial! We've got Bradberrys, we've got Persins, we've even got Papa himself. Court is back in session!
